Psionic_Blast.help: You fire a psionic burst at the target, causing damage and increasing recharge time.
Psionic_Blast.targetHelp: Your recharge rate has been reduced!

Psionic_Crush.help: You imprison your target in a field of collapsing psionic energy. They are held in place and suffer continuous damage and endurance loss.
Psionic_Crush.targetHelp: You are suffering psionic damage over time and losing endurance!

messages.attackerHit: You hit {PlayerDest} with your {PowerName} for {Damage} points of Psionic damage over time.

Psionic_Torment.help: You create painful visions within the mind of your target, and these visions manifest as bleeding wounds. When the visions end, the targets suffer reduced regeneration, recovery and recharge rate.
Psionic_Torment.targetHelp: You are suffering lethal damage and endurance loss over time. Additionally, your regeneration, recovery and recharge rate have been reduced.

messages.victimHit: {PlayerSource} creates unrelenting torment within your mind, causing {Damage} points of psionic damage.
Your mind makes the pain of {PlayerSource}'s {PowerName} real, causing {Damage} points of lethal damage and draining your endurance.

Psionic_Drift.help: You induce a dream state in all nearby targets around you while also dealing continuous psionic damage. These dreams can manifest as nightmares, lucid dreams or deep sleep, which manifest as fear, confusion or stun.
Psionic_Drift.shortHelp: PBAoE, High DMG (Psionic), Minor DoT (Psionic), Stun/Fear/Confuse(Foe)
Psionic_Drift.targetHelp: You are suffering psionic damage over time and are either feared, confused or stunned.

messages.victimHit: {PlayerSource} causes your mind to be affected by {PowerName}, inducing weakness and causing {Damage} points of psionic damage!
You continue to suffer {Damage} points of psionic damage while your mind is trapped in {PowerName}.

Psionic_Pulse.help: You unleash a powerful psionic shockwave that ripples through the air around you, dealing Psionic and Smashing damage to any hit by the wave. The shockwave also has a chance to knockback its targets.
Psionic_Pulse.targetHelp: You are knocked off your feet!

Psionic_Blade.help: You create a blade of crystalline psionic energy around your hand and use it to stab your target with a quick attack. The target suffers psionic damage, followed by a bleeding wound and reduced defense.
Psionic_Blade.shortHelp: Melee, Moderate DMG(Psionic), Moderate DoT (Lethal), -Def(Foe, All)

Psionic_Thrust.help: You create a blade of crystalline psionic energy around your hand and viciously stab your target. The target suffers psionic damage, followed by a bleeding wound and reduced resistance to further psionic damage.

Psionic_Thrust.targetHelp: You are bleeding and suffering from reduced resistance to psionic damage.
